::KitKat::
She looked at the component, then up to Phobia. "He was one of us. 
He's an old friend of Quickstrikes.  He helped us rescue Quickstrike 
from the Vok cave.  But Rowdy was caught by the vok and changed into 
one of them.  He's now talking to Megatron."  she drained the energon 
and stood up on all fours. "Any ideas on this?"

it
